isPublic.label: loki fakapule'anga
isPublic.description: 'E lava ke fekumi 'a e ngaahi loki fakapule'anga 'e he kau faka'aonga'i kehe .

allowGuestJoin.label: Tuku ke kau mai ʻa e kau ʻaʻahí .
allowGuestJoin.description: Fakaʻatā ʻa e kau fakaʻaongaʻi ʻoku ʻikai lesisitá ke nau kau ki he lokí ko ha fakaafe .

isEncrypted.label: Fakaʻatā ʻa e fakapulipuli ʻo e ngataʻangá ki he ngataʻangá .
isEncrypted.description: ‘I hono faka‘atā, ‘e fakapulipuli‘i ‘a e ngaahi pōpoaki ‘i he lokí ‘i he ngata‘anga ki he ngata‘angá .
isEncrypted.alert: Ko e fakapulipuli faka‘osí ‘oku faka‘atā ia ‘i he lokí, pea ‘oku ‘ikai lava ke tāmate‘i ‘a e tu‘unga ko ení.

form.submit: Fakahaofi ʻa e ngaahi tuʻunga fakapulipuli .

toast.success: Kuo fakafo'ou 'a e ngaahi tu'unga fakataautaha .
toast.error: Ta'elava ke fakafo'ou 'a e ngaahi tu'unga fakapulipuli .
